t-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">海莉·威廉姆斯（Hayley Williams）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特（St. Vincent）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">芬内亚斯（Finneas）</a>等人宣布为洛杉矶野火进行新的福利音乐会，“ g*ve af*ck”  - 查看下面的完整阵容。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="840" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259"><b>洛杉矶音乐社区告诉我们有关野火的“悲惨”影响：“这将被感受多年”</b></a></li></ul><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶被五个并发野火席卷，这些野火造成了前所未有的破坏</a>- 迄今为止，有15万名居民被迫撤离他们的家中，据报道有28例死亡和22名失踪人员。</p><p> 2月5日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的好莱坞钯中宣布了一场名为“ g*ve af*ck la”的新福利音乐会。除了威廉姆斯，圣文森特和芬内亚斯外，其他宣布表演的行为还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">露西·达科斯</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">穆纳</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/perfume-genius">香水天才</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-linda-lindas">琳达·琳达斯</a>，幻影星球，考特尼·巴内特，克里斯托弗·欧文斯，雷吉·瓦茨等。 </p><figure id="attachment_3802313" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802313" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802313" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hayley-williams@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802313" class="wp-caption-text">帕拉莫尔的海莉·威廉姆斯。图片来源：Gareth Cattermole/tas24/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>音乐会将由演员约翰·莱利（John C. Riley）主持，据说包括“惊喜来宾”和Harmony Tividad和Fat Tony的DJ套装。音乐会结束后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rico-nasty">Rico Nasty</a>和Dylan Brady将举办正式的聚会。</p><p>门票将于今天（1月28日）在太平洋的下午12点开始销售，无法亲自参加的球迷将能够通过Veeps以至少5美元的捐款来播放活动 - <a href="https://concerts.livenation.com/event/0900623759800A57?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaYd37ZE-YObmI461ScSzP7nkOKsJZtx3siI5gqWIT_2uOcBz273ecc_Ovs_aem__W978vMsC2kKt0XYYkLNgQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到更多</a>。</p><h3> <strong>“ g*ve af*ck la”福利音乐会是：</strong></h3><p><strong>克里斯托弗拥有</strong><br /><strong>考特尼·巴内特（Courtney Barnett）</strong><br /> <strong>Finneas</strong><br /><strong>弗雷德·阿米森</strong><br /><strong>海莉·威廉姆斯</strong><br /><strong>珍妮·刘易斯</strong><br /><strong>朱丽叶·刘易斯（Juliette Lewis）</strong><br /><strong>凯文·莫比（Kevin Morby）</strong><br /><strong>露西·达克斯（Lucy Dacus）</strong><br /><strong>穆纳</strong><br /><strong>香水天才</strong><br /><strong>幻影行星</strong><br /><strong>雷吉·瓦茨（Reggie Watts）</strong><br /> <strong>Sasami + Rostam</strong><br /><strong>侦察威利斯</strong><br /><strong>圣文森特</strong><br /><strong>琳达·琳达斯（Linda Lindas）</strong><br /> <strong>Symone</strong> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFWZx4OS8Ow/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41