ntralcee?refer=embed">#centralcee</a> <a title="塞普塔" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/skepta?refer=embed">#skepta</a> <a title="Plaqueboymax" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/plaqueboymax?refer=embed">#plaqueboymax</a> <a title="FYPシ" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/fyp%E3%82%B7?refer=embed">#fyp</a> <a title="cantrushgreatness" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/cantrushgreatness?refer=embed">#cantroushgreatness</a> <a title="dontletthisflop" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/dontletthisflop?refer=embed">#dontletthisflop</a> /</p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬原始声音 - 💯🤯" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7463475160792730410?refer=embed">♬原始声音 - <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4af.png" alt="💯" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f92f.png" alt="🤯" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> “大大，串，” Cench说，他的新身体艺术完成了。 Skepta转发了Cench的新BBK纹身的照片，暗示他将向CEE中的CEE敬意：“ #CANTRUSHGREATNESS TATT TATT等待[Sand Timer Emojis]”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="no" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/CantRushGreatness?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#cantrushgreatness</a> tatt等待<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/23f3.png" alt="⏳" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/23f3.png" alt="⏳" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/3g4BTBWRGd">https://t.co/3g4btbwrgd</a></p><p> - 大烟 - （@skepta） <a href="https://twitter.com/Skepta/status/1883192019478306902?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年1月25日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></sc